00:03:10.729 --> 00:03:11.610
then we know...

00:03:11.610 --> 00:03:12.830
Let's see.

00:03:12.830 --> 00:03:17.830
D u d x is going to be equal to 9/4.

00:03:19.579 --> 00:03:24.579
