00:06:07.117 --> 00:06:12.117
This is going to be equal to
2/3 times 4/9 is equal to 8/27.

00:06:15.355 --> 00:06:17.176
I've just factored out the 2/3.

00:06:17.176 --> 00:06:19.777
And then we're gonna have 27 minus one

00:06:19.777 --> 00:06:23.274
inside, I guess you could
say the brackets now.

00:06:23.274 --> 00:06:28.274
So 27 minus one is just going to be 26.

00:06:29.803 --> 00:06:32.157
Times 26.

